snippet.title: ASMR Food Experience: Playtest - Gameplay Trailer | STEAM
snippet.description:
Play the ASMR Food Experience Playtest on November 24, 2023! 🎧 Sign up now on Steam! 👇
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2066740/ASMR_Food_Experience/

In the ASMR Food Experience, you play the role of the owner of a small restaurant. 👨‍🍳 Some of your tasks in this simulator will be customer service but the most important is to listen to your own restaurant! 🎧 We have connected the game with the tones of the world around us. 🎵

---
#ASMR #ASMRFood #satisfying
